{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 461.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can stay here until, you know, you find the relatives and whatever it is because we got all this made-- you know, ready for you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we find, you know, all the other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was specially a man that now, later on, become my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at the time, he was just a friend from Rhodes Island.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was very, very friendly with my eldest sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to play cards in Rhodes Island before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he lost his wife and his children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His name is Giuseppe Malel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We find them, all the other ones-- they were thin, they were fed, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you can recognize them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This man, he was so thin, so different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, I say-- I said to the girls, who else is here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Giuseppe Malel, that is him, this, and this, and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Say, where is Giuseppe Malel?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He say, I'm Giuseppe Malel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You are Giuseppe-- you are not Giuseppe Malel, because we cannot believe it was him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His face was completely possible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His hair is grey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was another person, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many people, you know, they still-- you know-- they-- you know, you can recognize them a little bit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this person was unbelievable, the way he has changed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed there, you know, in this community for nearly one year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, you know, by the time we're there, you know, there the magazines and the newspapers, and the radio was announcing every day that Jewish refugees from Rome, from Italy, from Rhodes Island, are start coming back from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Among the other, you know, people, there were our names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now everybody-- we had these two brothers in the Belgian Congo.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
